**Objective**  
Translate the **editor screen layout**: video preview, playback controls, and the surrounding chrome that exists in Electron today—**only** that.

**What to translate**

- **Electron references:** [`old-electron/src/components/video-editor/VideoEditor.tsx`](../old-electron/src/components/video-editor/VideoEditor.tsx), [`old-electron/src/components/video-editor/VideoPlayback.tsx`](../old-electron/src/components/video-editor/VideoPlayback.tsx), [`old-electron/src/components/video-editor/PlaybackControls.tsx`](../old-electron/src/components/video-editor/PlaybackControls.tsx).
- **Behaviors to preserve:** Loading the current video (and optional webcam path) after recording or open-file, play/pause, time display, and navigation into export/settings entry points as they exist today.

**Status:** Non démarré

